Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: scandir
Version: 0.9
Summary: scandir, a better directory iterator that returns all file info the OS provides
Home-page: https://github.com/benhoyt/scandir
Author: Ben Hoyt
Author-email: benhoyt@gmail.com
License: New BSD License
Description: scandir is a generator version of os.listdir() that returns an iterator over files in a directory, and also exposes the extra information most OSes provide while iterating files in a directory. Read more at the GitHub project page.
